name: ayawmobiliko.com
overview:
Established in 2012, ayawmobiliko.com -buy and sell manila philippines, is an online classified advertisement website targeting users in the Philippines. Although most advertisers are local, we have advertisers and buyers coming from all over the world who have successfully used our classified ads services to satisfy their requirements. We give more value to Free advertisements by giving them guaranteed free banner exposures. Paid advertisements are assisted by helping their advertisement rank well in first pages of online search results. We care for ourt customers and innovation and loyalty to our customers is our key to our success.

Ayawmobiliko in filipino typically means, you don’t want it we buy from you or simply -you sell we buy. We offer this unique service wherein we have a 24 hours support staff that entertain sellers selling almost anything. We have positive feedbacks wherein desperate sellers needing cash for emergencies were able to sell to us in a matter of hours. This is mainly the idea of why we offer this unique service of ours.
